    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: 8/2/54",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, WFO (62-0)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "SUBJECT: [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "This interview is predicated upon a telephone call received by [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "SAC L. L. LAUGHLIN on 7/29/54 from [REDACTED] Bureau of",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Aeronautics, U. S. Navy Department.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "On the same date [REDACTED] was interviewed in Room 2912, Main",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Navy Building. Also present during the interview was [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "[REDACTED] and [REDACTED] furnished the following information:",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "They advised that the Office of Naval Intelligence had forwarded",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "a file to the Bureau of Aeronautics with enclosures which had been received",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "from [REDACTED] Accord-",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "ing to [REDACTED] and [REDACTED] resided near [REDACTED] who",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "had been receiving messages through thought transmission. [REDACTED] approached b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "[REDACTED] and advised him that \"flying saucers\" were here to help mankind.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Information received by [REDACTED] indicated that [REDACTED] became interested",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "in the messages received by [REDACTED] and felt that the matter should be",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "investigated by the Government.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "[REDACTED] advised that [REDACTED] wrote to Admiral ESPEY, Director",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "of Naval Intelligence, on 6/1/54 enclosing some of the messages received",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "by [REDACTED] Receiving no reply to his original communication, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "again wrote ONI on 6/7/54. [REDACTED] advised that the first letter that b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "[REDACTED] wrote to ONI contained information that [REDACTED] was receiving",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "messages through thought control from \"outer space\" and wrote them down",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "as she received them. The letter, according to [REDACTED], stated that [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "[REDACTED] would write without any effort on her part and would write continuously",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "for four or five hours at a time without getting tired. He stated that ONI",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "had in their possession the transmissions or messages that had been received",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "by [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "[REDACTED] stated that ONI had advised that in the absence of any b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "definite evidence of conversations, they would do nothing in the matter.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "He also stated that the Bureau of Aeronautics took no official action in",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
